{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"@property"},{"kind":"text","text":" ("},{"kind":"keyword","text":"nonatomic"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"assign"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"BOOL","preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@BOOL"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"rotatesToMatchCamera"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"languages":["occ"],"platforms":["iOS"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"discussion","level":2,"text":"Discussion","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"When the value of this property is "},{"code":"YES","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" and the map is rotated, the annotation"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"view rotates. This is also the behavior of "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationImage","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" objects. When the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"value of this property is "},{"code":"NO","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" the annotation has its rotation angle fixed."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The default value of this property is "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NO"},{"type":"text","text":". Set this property to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"YES"},{"type":"text","text":" if the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"view’s rotation is important."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"kind":"symbol","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView"]]},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView\/rotatesToMatchCamera"},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":